# ============================================================
# First recorded live sessions, 2026-07-16 (tools/session-analyzer).
# REPORT-ONLY cases NOT scenarioed:
#  * "stökklrikanum" → "stökkleikanum": the intended word is OOV in EVERY
#    vocabulary source we ship — is.lex unattested AND absent from BÍN
#    (unregistered compound stökk+leiki; even "stökkleiki" is BÍN-unknown,
#    while "sveigjanleikanum" is known). No ranking rule can surface a
#    candidate no lexicon contains; needs the compound-splitter wave
#    (PLAN.md "Compounds") or personal learning.
#  * "Kirkjubæjarklaustri" completion offered where "…dundra okkur á X"
#    wanted accusative "Kirkjubæjarklaustur": split-case governors should
#    surface both case variants of a lemma in the completion pool —
#    Stage B inflection follow-up.
# ============================================================

SCENARIO live session 2026-07-16 sentence-initial Fair restores to Fáir
# The capital F is AUTOCAP (sentence-initial after "Jökli."); skeleton
# "fair" is en.lex-attested (+0.57), so this runs the lane-weighted
# validity machinery — triple gate + sletta guard — at the
# boundary-DECAYED posterior (P(IS) ≈ 0.74), the least-defended position
# (no bigram, decayed lane). slettaGuardBlendThreshold 0.25 was
# calibrated on exactly this replay (advantage +0.47 vs the old 0.5 bar).
# Buffer updated 2026-07-16 (v→ð confusion wave): "sivan" now correctly
# restores to "síðan" (the session's intent — the analyzer flagged it as
# unreachable), and with prev="síðan" the "fra" repair loses its relaxed
# margin to the genuine bigram rival "síðan fram" (0.35 < 0.5) — an
# honest under-fire, frá stays offered in the bar.
T "Langar sivan fra Jökli. Fair"
EXPECT_AUTOCORRECT Fáir
T " "
EXPECT_BUFFER "Langar síðan fra Jökli. Fáir "

SCENARIO live session 2026-07-16 fa restores to fá at a saturated lane
